          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Our candles can help you relax and make your home smell amazing after a busy day. They're perfect for creating a calm space to unwind or hang out with friends.</p><h2>Scented Candles We Offer:</h2><ol><li><a href=\"/products/candle\" title=\"Luxe Natural Scented Candle in Emerald Green Jar\"><strong>Green Jar Candle</strong></a></li></ol><ul><li>Looks super cool on your shelf</li><li>Makes your room smell great</li></ul><ol><li><a href=\"/products/luxe-natural-scented-candle-in-amber-jar\" title=\"Luxe Natural Scented Candle in Amber Jar\"><strong>Amber Jar Candle</strong></a></li></ol><ul><li>Gives off a warm, cozy light</li><li>Perfect for chilling in your room</li></ul><h3>Awesome Scented Smells include:</h3><ul><li>Tiger Lily Lychee: Smells like flowers and fruit</li><li>Ice Lemon Biscotti: Like fresh lemons and cookies</li><li>Cedar Sandalwood: Woodsy smell, like being in a forest</li><li>Jasmine Neroli: Fancy flower smell that'll make you feel special</li></ul><h3>Why Our Candles Are Special</h3><ul><li>Made from soy wax, which is better for the environment</li><li>Burns for a long time, so you get more for your money</li><li>Comes in pretty jars you can use for other stuff later</li><li>Smells so good, your friends will want to know where you got them</li></ul><h3>How to Get Your Scented Candle From Mumu Bath:</h3><ol><li>Pick your favorite smell</li><li>Choose green or amber jar</li><li>Add to cart</li><li>Check out and wait for your awesome candle to arrive!</li></ol><p>Get Your Cool Candle Now!</p><p>Click 'Add to Cart' to make your room the best-smelling place ever. Your friends will be jealous!</p>"
